state.title: default
state.stateText: Liberation will give rise to a new protectorate in the region, loyal to your nation whilst diplomatic relations are strong.

state.title: spa_napoleon

state.title: default
state.stateText: Resources permitting, a force of conscripts will be granted to the liberating army on behalf of the new protectorate.

state.title: spa_napoleon
state.stateText: In recognition of your efforts to rid their lands of their enemies, a small force of local fighters will join your ranks to aid you in your campaign.

state.title: Neutral
state.tooltip: Feeling neutral||This is the higher class public order.||Your higher class are currently neither angry nor happy.||Applying a little extra repression will improve their public order.||This is based on the positive and negative factors to the right.

state.title: Happy
state.tooltip: Under control||This is the higher class public order.||Your higher class are currently under control.||This is based on the positive and negative factors to the right.

state.title: Angry
state.tooltip: Angry||This is the higher class public order.||Your higher class are angry and are likely to cause trouble!||Try to placate the protesting populace by exempting the region from tax or increasing repression!||This is based on the positive and negative factors to the right.

state.title: Neutral
state.tooltip: Feeling neutral||This is the lowest class public order.||Your lowest class are currently neither angry nor happy.||They could go either way at the moment - improving repression a little will improve their public order.||This is based on the factors to the right.

state.title: Happy
state.tooltip: Under control||This is the lowest class public order.||Your lowest class are currently under control.||They are either very happy, very repressed or a little of both!||This is based on the factors to the right.

state.title: Angry
state.tooltip: Angry||This is the lowest class public order.||Your lowest class are currently angry and likely to riot.||Try increasing repression or exempting this region from tax to prevent rioting!||This is based on the factors to the right.

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: Peaceful occupation will result in minor damage to military buildings within the settlement.
